fields.name: Rolex
fields.about: Known for its prestigious status and iconic models like the Submariner and Date just, Rolex is synonymous with luxury and quality. It was founded in 1905 and is celebrated for innovations like the first waterproof wristwatch, the Oyster

fields.name: Omega
fields.about: Famous for the Speedmaster, the first watch on the moon, Omega combines technical excellence with stylish designs. The brand has a rich history dating back to 1848

fields.name: Audemars Piguet
fields.about: Renowned for the Royal Oak, Audemars Piguet has been a pioneer in luxury sports watches since its founding in 1875. The brand is known for its innovative designs and high-quality craftsmanship

fields.name: Seiko
fields.about: A Japanese brand recognized for its reliability and craftsmanship, Seiko offers a wide range of watches, from affordable quartz models to high-end mechanical pieces

fields.name: Casio
fields.about: Known for its durable and affordable watches, Casio's G-Shock line is particularly popular for its ruggedness and functionality

fields.name: Citizen
fields.about: This brand is known for its eco-friendly technology and innovative designs, making it a popular choice among consumers looking for value

fields.name: MTP-VT01LM-7A
fields.description:
Classic and compelling. An analog watch with a sophisticated marble-inspired dial.

Water resistance for daily use frees you from worry, even on rainy days.
